          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The yield  curves  and  cross  sections for reactions",
                " 113In(gamma,gamma')113mIn (T1/2=99.4 min., JPI=1/2-),",
                " 195Pt(gamma,gamma')195mPt (T1/2=4.02 days, JPI=13/2+)",
                " and  199Hg(gamma,gamma')199mHg (T1/2=42.6 min., JPI =",
                " 13/2+) were obtained.  113In(gamma,gamma')113mIn",
                " reaction cross section has maximum at energy about",
                " 9.0 MeV, but those for 195Pt(gamma,gamma')195mPt and",
                " 199Hg(gamma,gamma')199mHg at about 6.4 MeV.  The",
                " resonance positions for all nuclei investigated",
                " coincide  with the appropriate (gamma,n) reaction",
                " thresholds."
              ]
            }
          ],
